t-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14.44444465637207px; line-height: 26.99652862548828px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">与心相依，爱与爱永恒。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.wmpic.me/57062/568c7ee278d7f_37\"><img src=\"http://p3.wmpic.me/article/2016/01/06/1452048098_LnSYHgIv.jpg\" alt=\"\"/></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14.44444465637207px; line-height: 26.99652862548828px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">用一份真心的付出，在文字暖语，总会让久违的心感动，在真情笔尖，总会令相知</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14.44444465637207px; line-height: 26.99652862548828px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">的心陶醉</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.wmpic.me/57062/568c7ee27fa2a_47\"><img src=\"http://p3.wmpic.me/article/2016/01/06/1452048098_XZoaflDV.jpg\" alt=\"\"/></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14.44444465637207px; line-height: 26.99652862548828px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">真情于心灵交汇，快乐与喜悦分享，听一曲琴音，拾一段心情，一字一句，恰似你</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14.44444465637207px; line-height: 26.99652862548828px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">的轻轻呢喃。</span></p>            ' ,`seo_title` = '' ,`seo_keywords` = '' ,`seo_description` = '' ;
